_sText:
A simple jacuzzi prefab, nothing too detailed. 

Green-on
Red-off

When you turn on the jacuzzi the smoke and stream come out to make it seem more like a jacuzzi.

The first time you turn on the jacuzzi, some of the smoke stacks may not work.  Just turn the jacuzzi off and then turn it back on and it should work. Unless someone can tell me how to fix this, then its going to have to stay the way it is for now.

If youd like, put my name in the credits if you use it in your map. If not its fine
